# Server-side 301 redirects (Cloudflare Pages). Local astro dev/preview does
# not honor this file, so root renders the zh landing page directly while
# /{lang}/guide/ keeps a meta-refresh fallback for old links.
#
# Phase 10.1 — kills white-screen flash from
# `<a>Redirecting from <code>/</code> to <code>/zh/</code></a>` body text.

/                /zh/                       301
/zh/guide        /zh/guide/user-guide/      301
/zh/guide/       /zh/guide/user-guide/      301
/en/guide        /en/guide/user-guide/      301
/en/guide/       /en/guide/user-guide/      301
/ja/guide        /ja/guide/user-guide/      301
/ja/guide/       /ja/guide/user-guide/      301
